-- Pick n Pay Signs Up 4 Million to Loyalty Program, Times Says
-- B y   M i k e   C o h e n
-- 2012-01-08T09:51:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-08/pick-n-pay-signs-up-4-million-to-loyalty-program-times-says.html
Pick n Pay Stores Ltd. (PIK)  has signed 4
million customers to its loyalty program, which offers discounts
on some product lines and other benefits,  Business Times 
reported, citing the South African retailer’s Chief Executive
Officer Nick Badminton.  Pick n Pay is “very happy” with current growth,
especially that experienced last month, Badminton said,
according to the Johannesburg-based newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mike Cohen in  Cape Town  at 
 mcohen21@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
